data.title: 7th Infantry Battalion
data.meta_description: The shield commemorates those from the 7th Infantry Battalion who served in World War One, World War Two and the Vietnam War.
data.text:
Front Inscription

7th Battalion 2/7th Battalion

Australian Imperial Force Australian Imperial Force

Cede Nullis Cede Nullis

(Battle Campaigns) (Battle Campaigns)

7th Battalion the Royal Australian Regiment

This shield is dedicated to the soldiers of

7th Battalion Australian Imperial Force

2/7th Battalion Australian Imperial Force

7th Battalion Royal Australian Regiment

Who gave their lives in

The Great War of 1914 - 1918

The World War of 1939 -1945

Vietnam 1967 -1968

1971 -1972

"Lest We Forget "

Dedicated by

The Rector Rev. R. V. Ash

in the Garrison Church,

The Rocks, Sydney

14th November 1976
